{"tid":1222534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】英外相直接向林鄭月娥對話籲聽市民意見","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T12:51:36.000Z","uid":50457,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e295c79397a1e77e5b431d3c4ff8c41ce2f79a7","tid":1222534,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"英國國會下議院再度辯論香港《修訂逃犯》條例草案，英國外交部亞太事務國務大臣田銘祺表示，外相侯俊偉星期四已直接向香港行政長官林鄭月娥表達關注，呼籲港府聆聽市民意見，採取措施維護香港高度自治、權利和自由。<br />\n田銘祺指，香港市民對政府修訂逃犯條例，反應強烈，毫無疑問造成廣泛影響，敦促香港政府與本地和國際持份者對話，而港府應暫緩修例，強調《中英聯合聲明》簽署30年至今仍然有效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1023061-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%90%91%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1%E7%B1%B2%E8%81%BD%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1023061-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E8%2581%25BD%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25A6%258B&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=fedd1ce9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1023061-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E8%2581%25BD%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25A6%258B&h=3c6bf069\" target=\"_blank\">h